r>
&lt;Once more, upon the infamous halls of the path of the prince of Hate, was the way she took. Simply to bring some memories, to a ever ending pain in which she never let go, the pain that leaving a family may endure.&gt;<br>
<br>
*The door but simply cracked as a metalic lady entered her silent shadow within the halls of the Harvest. Her shade never changed with the age, but the heart always grew toward a deeper sorrow. She started to walk for the surely last time, in the ever dark tunnels of the city of Neriak*<br>
<br>
*Standing infront of a old but now occupied house, she leans toward the opposing wall, watching the ever crumbling house of the Great Priestess, the school of the Teachings of Hate. A little breath, all filled with the cold air*<br>
<br>
And there the lady explained herself :&quot;From honestly through my heart filled with hate, I must say this house miss me, to where i could speak with my teacher, my mother and my master... *Look around* I will go through, memories never killed anyone...&quot;<br>
<br>
*And then, the lady entered the empty building, extremely surprised she speaks to herself :&quot;Where are the cries? The call of despairs...&quot; And then she sat foot on the hall which leads to the rooms. To here was her more deadly pain, to discover the names of the old Triad disapeared...*<br>
<br>
&quot;How can it be... The Mother even is gone?... Wonders to see who will replace her. To see Master Khasirath taking the place of Mistress Creapiing is no surprise, and good news. *But then, as a flow of tears began to leave her eyes, as she saw the room of Master Vinar, empty...* By the name of our Father, this can not be, why dear?... Why... where... I will not believe that the immortal one has ever fell to any lightborns or whatever the cause may be... This is the worse.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;This place as greatly changed, and so have we... I suppose a meeting must happen soon, wonders... &quot; *On those words, the lady turned back... And took the last hall, which led to the Priests rooms* &quot;Nospiratus... You managed to stay alive even through all this, you are truely my Teacher, I hope you will forgive my manners and errors, to change my own path. I know leaving the side of the Harvest was the worse thing to do, but frequently, we need to see some thing else, of which i have done. *Look at the room infront of the Mad Prophet`s room...* My room havent changed at all, still so red... /sigh... I will leave now before i flood this temple of my tears...&quot;<br>
<br>
*Of this she left a message to the &quot;new&quot; Reaper, <br>
<br>
&quot;To his moment i broke my heart, as to see my life go away. I pledge you not to forgive me but to hunt me, as far as i go, for i have broken my oath to our Father, as the Harvest shall not occur within my own hands, but only yours, my soul has left his side, but not my heart... To see this is not enough for your forgiveness. Trust my Master Khasirath, the Violent Harvest shall see night, as an ally or an enemy of the Sad Rose, The Priestess of Sadness shall always see foward the love of your family&quot;<br>
<br>
On this letter was signed,<br>
&quot;Lady TristRose,<br>
 High head Priestess of Innoruuk,<br>
 Last of the line of the Sad Rose,<br>
<br>
<br>
 Cheldra TristRose <p><center><img src=http://www.multimania.com/alfadar/signaturelylys.jpg></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=320.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=320.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=320.topic><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/harvest/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=320.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.threadControl?topicID=320.topic><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/harvest/skull.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=320.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=320.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub79.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><